-- can never cache wrongly-empty. 500s/timeouts simply re-fire as stragglers.
--
-- HOW IT WORKS: stage centroids -> fire the live engine via pg_net in ~90-ZIP
-- waves -> collect with the transient-safe upsert -> re-fire stragglers ->
-- app_refresh_all(). Run statements SEPARATELY; wait ~160s between fire/collect.
